":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T14:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>近排跟同事飲下紅酒，以為紅酒係法國先靚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但呢排人地介紹飲下意大利，發現原來都唔錯同平好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打討論下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4v78i2cp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4v78i2cp&h=694b28f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西班牙都好多正酒又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班朋友呢排飲意大利多，我都係同朋友學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dnork74e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdnork74e&h=7efd3d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西班牙，La Rioja Alta gran reserva 904，抵飲，不過要時間breathe。<br />\n<br />\n意大利我鍾意Tuscany既酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079c7a413288aebe28379ee5479291cc0014cf99","tid":260612,"uid":39604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T15:35:19.000Z","msg":"有冇759買到的紅酒介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e8f2e65e659b3b1cd3ec929cd8e57cf6ec2947","tid":260612,"uid":6733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白酒可以試下elena walch Pinot Grigio 2015都唔錯，又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平白酒放兩年口感都好清新，百幾蚊貨仔算幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢支平靚正，夏天飲一流。1881飲第1次，回味無窮，專登上網搵。依家1881都收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29804716a8cb8c7b0d7d6be56811f5278ddbb55","tid":260612,"uid":6733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T15:46